<page>
   <topic>A5_CONTROL_DELETE_IMAGE Function</topic>
   <syntax>V a5_control_delete_image(P obj [,C type ])</syntax>
   <arguments>
     <argument>
         <name>obj</name>
         <description>Pointer</description>
     </argument>
     <argument>
         <name>type</name>
         <description>A pointer to an image control on a form.</description>
     </argument>
   </arguments>
   <description>Public user defined function.</description>
   <discussion>
The A5_CONTROL_DELETE_IMAGE() function displays a dialog that allows you to confirm the deletion of an image file in an image reference field.

   </discussion>
   
   <sections>
       <section>
       <title>Example</title>
            <description>The following script was placed under a button on a form with an image reference field named Image1.</description>
            <example><![CDATA[
a5_control_delete_image(parentform:Image1.this)
]]></example>
       </section>
   </sections>
   <limitations>Desktop applications only.</limitations>
